# Git Workflow (Opus 4.6)

## Principle

Three branch tiers: `main` (stable), `dev` (developer), `agent` (agent).
**Opus works in `dev`. User commits. Merge to main via consensus.**

---

## Branch Model

```
main                    # Stable, deployed on RPi. Merge-only.
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ dev                 # Developer works here (Cursor + Opus)
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ agent               # Agent's primary branch (RPi)
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ agent/skills    # Agent sub-branch (if needed)
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ agent/evolve-N  # Evolution cycle branch
```

Flow:
```
dev ‚îÄ‚îÄconsensus‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí main ‚îÄ‚îÄpull‚îÄ‚îÄ‚Üí agent
                    ‚Üë                ‚îÇ
                    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ consensus ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò
```

Merge to main: requires consensus of developers + model review.

---

## Opus Rules

### MAY

- `git status`, `git diff`, `git log` ‚Äî read-only
- `git add` ‚Äî when user requests

### MUST NOT

- `git commit`, `git push`, `git merge`, `git rebase`

---

## Developer Workflow (in `dev`)

```
1. Work in dev branch
2. Opus edits, user commits
3. When ready: consensus merge dev ‚Üí main
4. Agent detects main update, pulls into agent
```

---

## Commit Message Format

```
type: description

Details if needed
```

Types: `test`, `code`, `refactor`, `fix`, `docs`, `rule`

---

## File Ownership

| Owner | Scope | Agent may |
|-------|-------|-----------|
| Developer | `src/agent/core.py`, `src/cli.py`, `src/utils/` | Read-only |
| Developer | `.cursor/`, `agent_rules/core-constitution.md` | Read-only |
| Agent | `src/skills/`, `src/agent/prompts/`, `src/agent/config/` | Full control |
| Agent | `tests/agent_tests/` | Full control (own tests) |
| Agent | `agent_rules/runtime/` | Modify within bounds |
| Shared | `CHANGELOG.md` | Append-only |
| Protected | `agent_rules/core-constitution.md` | NEVER modify |
